summary: An updated version of the RND USKP Compatibility patch to be compatible with USLEEP
descriptionHtml:
An updated version of the original Realistic Needs and Diseases (RND) USKP Compatibility patch to be compatible with the new Unofficial Skyrim Legendary Edition Patch (USLEEP), instead of the now outdated USKP.

NOTE: THIS MOD IS FOR THE ORIGINAL RND, NOT RND 2!

I did not create this mod, I just made it compatible with USLEEP using [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71316]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71316[/url]

Links to the mods:

    - USLEEP: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71214]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71214[/url]
    - USKP: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/19]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/19[/url]
    - UDGP: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/23491]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/23491[/url]
    - UHFP: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/25127]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/25127[/url]
    - UDBP: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31083]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31083[/url]
